br.com.estudio89.syncing.serialization.annotations

Annotation Type JSON


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface JSON
    Created by luccascorrea on 6/20/15. The attribute writable, if false, means the attribute will not be written to the json object when serializing the Model object. The attribute readable, if false, means the attribute will not be read from the json object when deserializing the object.
